ComicInfo.Summary:
America's longest-running humor magazine continues to skewer everything pop culture! February's TV-themed issue is packed with new, original content and a wide variety of vintage MAD favorites (because so many boobs have been on the tube)! Featuring a new "The Shadow Knows" by Sergio Aragonés, a new Spy vs. Spy by Peter Kuper, and more, MAD will surely make the whole family laugh...while still managing to piss off some folks.
